Package: nucleoid
Architecture: amd64
Depends: nodejs, npm
Description: Declarative Runtime Environment
 Nucleoid is an open source (Apache 2.0), a runtime environment for declarative
 programming in ES6/JavaScript syntax and runs as a datastore. Since statements
 are declarative, the runtime automatically provides logical integrity,
 multiprocessing, plasticity, persistency etc.
